Big Brother Naija housemate, Kiddwaya has advised Praise on the next steps to take concerning Wathoni. Kiddwaya asked Praise on what he wanted to do with Wathoni. Responding, Praise on Friday night said that he really likes Wathoni. Kiddwaya on the other hand advised him to forget about outside for now, be himself around Wathoni and be nice to her. He said: “Be a gentleman with her, make her happy. “Show her your moves, treat her nice from tomorrow. Your fiancée gave you permission to do what you have to do in the house.”